This piece is more fluid and dramatic, with sweeping movement across the canvas. It uses deep indigo, navy blue, emerald green, smoky grey, pearl white and copper-gold highlights. The shapes flow into one another like ink, resin, marble, mineral veins, water currents, or a storm seen from above.
